Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫威《神盾局特工》前情回顧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Previously on "Marvel's Agents Of S.H.I.E.L.D."...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅  你的腿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May. Your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒完全恢復\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're still not 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's no way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是說了實話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can tell for certain if you're being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我和西蒙斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just me and Simmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們說的是實話  她們兩個都是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're telling the truth. Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你掩蓋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I covered for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你也可以讓別人讀到你的想法  -對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You can let other people read your mind, too. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個低溫冷凍艙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a Cryo-Freeze Chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走遠路過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm taking the long way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沉睡期間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}While you were asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得以展開了一項計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had time to put a plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我拿到賣了你的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With the price I'll fetch for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就終于可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll finally have the means
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠離開這個可怕的地方了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to leave this horrendous place once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是世界毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's the Destroyer of Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接讓她決戰生死吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She should fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能湊合下了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gonna have to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾琴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給你的盒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Got your tin right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出一個代幣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll give you a token.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A token?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為至少能換三個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was hoping for at least three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能出這么多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Token's all I can spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你是我最喜歡的客戶呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only for my favorite customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽徹斯  我今天還不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Citrus, look, ‭I don't have enough today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也許明天就能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but maybe tomorrow, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry, junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有贈品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No gimmes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你的施舍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I don't need charity, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你最好的報價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only your best offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在找你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯在繁育異人拿來賣錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius is breeding Inhumans to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有自己的恐怖科學部什么的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Guy's got his own cronenberg science division and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會來了這么多飛船\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This would explain all the ships arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他們是為了黛西而來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think they're here for Daisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有梅的消息嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And still no sign of May?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常來說  她對付得了克里人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Normally, she could hold her own against the Kree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的腿狀態不好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But her leg -- it's in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這里啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰絲  怎么了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tess, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍臉人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the Blues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來收孩子了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They've come to harvest the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是卡拉巴夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}{\*}That is Lady Karaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個瘋狂的野蠻人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She is a demented brute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對人的喜愛猶如詛咒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her affection a cursed to anyone who receives it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是參議員蓋烏斯·普納瑞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And there is Senator Gaius Ponarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他  就覺得反胃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am... repulsed by the sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連他最親近的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even the man's closest friends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也覺得他的脾氣就像一個有病的小野獸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}find his temperament to be that of a diseased child monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來卡塞亞斯真是聚集了最壞的人渣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seems Kasius has assembled the worst of the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害怕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比這間屋子里的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are far more reprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都更名聲狼藉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than any other creature in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了  伊諾克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for that, Enoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構建你的假身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a rather fun pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺有趣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}constructing your alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再是利奧波德·菲茲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No longer are you Leopold Fitz,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是  波什托克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but instead, Boshtok,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位擁有無盡財富的卑鄙太空掠奪者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a vile space Marauder of unlimited wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個胸牌真有必要嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was the brooch really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸牌代表了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That medal signifies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你取過的敵人性命數目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the number of enemy lives you've taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  感覺有點怪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just... seems a little odd
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著塊鑲了小水鉆的胸牌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}wearing a medal ‭with little rhinestones on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真逗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is quite amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定知道那是蓋格酷幼蟲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You no doubt realize those are Geg-ku larvae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  這樣吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們放下偽裝  找到其他人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's drop the charade, find the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后殺出一條血路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we'll shoot our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人存活的幾率\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The chances of survival would be less than 2%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將不到2%\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for each individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是珍瑪·西蒙斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is Jemma Simmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我安排介紹一下嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you like me to broker an introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什么需要你把我介紹給珍瑪·西蒙斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why would I need you to introduce me to Jemma Simmons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是掠奪者規矩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's Marauder protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這群貪婪鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look at the sniveling horde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些忘恩負義的家伙多年來一直嘲笑我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These same ingrates mocked me all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻聚在這里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}yet now they hover about,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵著要我青睞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}clamoring for my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這位掠奪者也不熟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I, too, am unfamiliar with the Marauder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說他非常富有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}though his fortune is rumored to be vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我多留意他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want me to keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普納瑞  再次見到你真好  親愛的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ponarian, how great to see you again, dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這里總是很榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a pleasure to be here as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的招待  卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for your hospitality, Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍瑪  是我  別轉身\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jemma, it's me. Don't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在一個秘密軍事監獄里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, I spent six months locked up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被關了六個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in an ‭off-the-books military prison --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用說在太空里冷凍了80年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not to mention 80 years frozen in space --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望能夠找到你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}all just hoping to find you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于見到你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想通了一件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙無法阻止我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The universe can't stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們跨越了星系  穿越了時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'Cause we've crossed galaxies. We've traveled through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在大西洋海底也活了下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've survived ‭the bottom of the Atlantic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為了能在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just so we could be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的愛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, a love like that --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何詛咒都強大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's stronger than any curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你和我  我們合力就不可阻擋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you and I -- we are unstoppable together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想和你分開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to live another day without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍瑪·西蒙斯  你愿意嫁給我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, Jemma Simmons, will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我說了要淡定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know -- I mean, ‭I know I said, "Play it cool,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是這么淡定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I didn't mean play it this cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍瑪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么問題嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問了你仆人一個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I asked your servant a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她沒理我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which she ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的仆人只能聽見主人的聲音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My servitors are only allowed to hear the voice of their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你跟我說說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, why don't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的奴隸聽不見客人說什么\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}how your guests' needs are met
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么滿足他們的需求呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when your slaves can't hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她堪稱楷模\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This one is quite exemplary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  她是和世界毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In fact, ‭she also traveled through time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起穿越時間過來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with the ‭Destroyer of Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能也是她膚色如此無暇的原因\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which probably explains her flawless complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她賣嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is she for sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單獨出售\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是捆綁項目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She comes as a companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她很擅長激勵毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for she is quite adept at motivating the Destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現  人們需要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I find the only motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一激勵就是痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}people ever really need is pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及對痛苦的正確利用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And its proper application.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有見地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A wonderful sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著這么引人矚目的胸牌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should have expected no less from a man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理當有如此見識\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with such an impressive brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need you to go see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的收成都有什么\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what has been reaped from today's harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么  地球的食物嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What? Terran food awaits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多  但收成指的是別的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A bounty, though the harvest is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早些時候  我的手下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Earlier today, my men were carrying out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主持了泰瑞根變異\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the process of Terrigenesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能為客人造出新的異人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}hoping to produce new Inhumans for my guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果客人有意的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If any were so inclined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得看買下毀滅者之后\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Depends on how many units I have left
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還剩多少錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}after I purchase the Destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說  你的品味很昂貴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is said you are a man of expensive tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就能知道你有沒有足夠的資本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We shall soon see if you have the resources
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足這種欲望了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to support such desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯都讓所有滿18歲的穿過泰瑞根迷霧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius puts all the 18-year-olds through Terrigenesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that day's today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是幾個月之前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, that was months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子還只是青少年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Most of these kids are barely teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是負責人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's the one in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從低層一點點往上抓人來著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Been working his way up from the lower floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜這跟卡塞亞斯的盛大派對有關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing this has something to do with Kasius' big party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產品多  利潤就多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More products, more profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是弗林特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's Flint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人跟他說話安慰他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't have anyone talking him through this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他父母在一次更新時被殺了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His parents were killed in a Renewal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維吉爾很喜歡這孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Virgil had a soft spot for the kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至教他如何飛行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}was even teaching him to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時不時給他點錢  幫他渡日\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gave him odds and ends to help him get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該去跟他說句話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should go say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰絲  這怎么回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tess, this is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該再有兩年才要穿過迷霧的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't supposed to get misted for another two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你不用再等了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just means you don't have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會毀了我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this gonna mess me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, everything is gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越迷霧  沒什么大不了的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Going through the mist -- it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有一群土狼盯著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Terrigenesis is scary enough
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞根變異也夠嚇人的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without a bunch of hyenas watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是他們的錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not their fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人全都被灌輸了同樣的謊言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These people have all been fed the same lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們相信自己想要相信的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People believe ‭what they want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然他們是要被送去屠宰的羔羊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's obvious they're lambs being led to the slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿這些孩子都不會結殼吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's just hope ‭none of these kids crust over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真轉變了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I do turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我不會再來向你要殘羹剩菜了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}least you won't have me coming around, begging for scraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like having you come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們  到時間了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Children, it is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們尋求恩賜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We seek a great bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望今天聚集在此的年輕人中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hoping that one of the young gathered here today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能自我升華\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}ascends to something greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備接受卡塞亞斯賜予你們的禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Prepare to receive your gift from Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗林特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Flint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你呢  -沒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}{\*}- Do you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賣給你的那窩維羅尼辛怎么樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, how are you faring with that Vrellnexian litter I sold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是挺難對付\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has been trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些野獸真是很難控制\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The savage beasts have proven quite difficult to wrangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可不是生來讓人抱的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, they're certainly not bred to cuddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是戰爭猛獸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're creatures of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人類毛茸茸的小狗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the not the shaggy dog of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我本希望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I had hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維羅尼辛會給你帶來小小的勝利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that the Vrells would provide you a small triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我們聊的時候  被流放的重擔似乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Last time we spoke, the strain of your exile seemed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的靈魂不堪重負\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}wear heavy on your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒被流放\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was never exiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親只是希望我親自監督他的地球計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My father simply wanted me to oversee his Earth project personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你哥哥則在監督家族帝國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}While your brother oversees the family empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯從未讓我做過戰士  直到今天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius never offered me as a fighter till today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這是我救你一命的下場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Guess that's what I get for saving your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒叫你救我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't ask you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我救你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were hoping for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子里是這么想的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對讀心人來說沒什么差別\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is basically the same thing for a mind-reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況開始有利于我們了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Things are starting to turn in our favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以相信我  行嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so just trust me on this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很慶幸我的抑制器現在開著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm really glad ‭my Inhibitor's on right now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就聽不到你腦子里的蠢主意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so I can't hear whatever dumb idea's in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We just need to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再以為你有什么選擇了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop thinking that you have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是奴隸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉將你卷了進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am sorry for getting you mixed up in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們不需要互相殘殺吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's just hope one of us doesn't have to kill the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的朋友們  卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dear friends, in honor of Kasius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為大家獻上了世界毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}presenting the Destroyer of Worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也為大家準備了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I, too, have brought a rare delicacy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一道珍貴的佳肴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for everyone's enjoyment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新鮮的山達爾蝸牛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}fresh Xandarian snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慷慨了  普納瑞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are far too generous, Ponarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等開始競價的時候  務必記住這一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please keep that in mind when the bidding begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么將這里的人口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you keep your human population
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制得這么好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so well under heel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讓他們自相殘殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He has them kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換我也會這么做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類顯然占大多數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Humans clearly have the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須讓他們恐懼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so fear is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最難辦的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And getting them to do it --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們來動手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that is the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀式化很有用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ritualization helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切粉飾成一場游戲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Making it sort of a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常有效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's all very efficient, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少就我的經驗而言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...at least in my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們所見略同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seems we have similar minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是非常有效地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has done wonders
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓制了人類反叛的沖動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}tamping down the humans' more rebellious impulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家都享受這頓宴席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I hope everyone's meal has been to their liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來即將進行的生死決戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As for your more primal appetites,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則能滿足你們最原始的欲望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a fight to the death is moments away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后看一眼他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, take a final look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一位異人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One of these Inhumans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要從市場上撤下來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}will soon be withdrawn from the marketplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠奪者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Marauder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒嘗你的蝸牛呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you have yet to taste your snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許低俗的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps unrefined men
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法領略此等珍饈的美味\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}don't have the stomach for such indulgences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I find...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮濕的生物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}moist creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很惡心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...distasteful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像將它們吞咽下去的肥嘴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...much like the fat mouths slurping them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這位波什托克一起用餐真有意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This Boshtok makes for a lively dinner companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先將這些蝸牛放在一邊吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let us leave these snails to shrivel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有更精彩的表演等著我們呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Much greater pursuits await our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那孩子的能力是消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe the boy's ability is to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這里面有鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, this is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有人就這樣消失了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How does someone just disappear like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不確定...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm really not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有個猜測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}though I may have a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們得回大集市  -那不安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We got to get back to The Exchange. - It's not safe for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但那些守衛會找我的  -是為了賣了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- But the Guards will be looking for me. - Only to sell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我能過得更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I get a better life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同層的人也能受益\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the rest of the level profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會過得更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You get no better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買下其他人的人都不是好人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People who buy other people are not good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只會傷害你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll only hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么做到的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-泰絲  -你沒事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- ‭Tess. - Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛被一個瘋女人綁架了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was just kidnapped by a crazy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點孩子可沒說錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the kid ain't wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  她和我是一起的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗林特  這是悠悠球  她也是異人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Flint, this is Yo-Yo. She's Inhuman, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多猜到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I kind of figured that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是住在克里人層嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why aren't you living down on the Kree levels?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這里的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not really from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}None of us are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是唯一和我們一起的異人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And she's not the only Inhuman with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他也是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他就這么氣派\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, he's just cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能永遠躲在這里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, we can't hide in here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會兒卡塞亞斯的人肯定在到處找弗林特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius' men will be looking for Flint even as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾去找站長匯報了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Grill's reporting to his station boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上他就會回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'll be back end of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得在那之前趕緊消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to disappear long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以申請拖曳船作業\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I could put in for a Trawler run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把弗林特藏在禁閉室里然后離開這里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We hide Flint in the brig and head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給我們爭取個幾天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Could buy us a couple days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有梅  我們沒有人能駕駛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but without May, we don't have a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Least of our worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫手嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Want any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人越多  越容易招疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More people, more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最好一個人去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Best I go on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Be back in a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這樣的人加入我們真令人耳目一新\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is refreshing ‭to have a man of your caliber join our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意和我一起觀看展示嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you care to join me for the upcoming display?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等不及見識你要給我們看的每個人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm eager to see everyone you have to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可得盡我所能不讓你失望了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I shall make every effort not to disappoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一位選手擁有無與倫比的能力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our first contestant possesses extraordinary skill --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈感應  他能感知對手的戰略\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a telepath, able to read his opponent's plan of attack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕對方尚未執行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before it is carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常我會讓本和其他異人對打\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Normally, I'd pit Ben against another Inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為了今天的貴客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yet, for this select crowd,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定挑選一位特別的對手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've decided for a more unique opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一位來自別的時空\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One not of this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練這位致命殺手的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This deadly assassin was trained
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是銀河系最臭名昭著的組織\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by one of the galaxy's most despised organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最有趣的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But most intriguing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是世界毀滅者的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}she is also a friend to the Destroyer of Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位貴賓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dear guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我向你們介紹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}may I present to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神盾局特工  梅琳達·梅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...Melinda May, Agent of S.H.I.E.L.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是作弊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}{\*}You're cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你就要死了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you're dying. ‭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少人和毀滅者一起穿越了時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many traveled in time with the Destroyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只發現了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My servant and Melinda May
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳達·梅和我的仆人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}are the only ones I've discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是錫納拉堅信還有更多人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}though Sinara remains convinced there are more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀心者打斗很熟練\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The mind reader's a skilled fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來訓練很刻苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Speaks well of his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本在異人中算天賦頗高的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ben is quite talented for an Inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他在我父親的軍隊里一天都活不下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he wouldn't last a day in my father's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對你父親的評價很高\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You speak highly of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我所知最偉大的戰士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's the greatest warrior I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽普納瑞的話  好像\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ponarian made it seem as if
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被從你的母星驅逐了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you'd been banished from your home world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普納瑞是不知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ponarian knows not of what he speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親就不看好我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My father was disapproving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到他的尊重  我做了不少事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The things I did to earn his respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了不少傷疤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...they left scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的故事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My own situation --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則是誤解帶來的悲劇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it is ‭a tragic misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒人能幫你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one can help you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連卡塞亞斯的客人都不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not even a guest of Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在懷疑自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're doubting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別刺探我的想法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stay out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你拍賣毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My guess is ‭you're selling the Destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了改變他的看法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as a way to redeem yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信大筆的財富\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I believe a great fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠撫平一切罪過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}can smooth over any transgression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意幫助你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm prepared to help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別覺得是我壞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't make me the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯把我扔進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius only tossed me in here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為我幫了你的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because I helped your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不殺你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你無謂的承諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for promising not to do something you can't --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有思考  直接動手了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Didn't think, just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎么那么看重團隊合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is it with you guys and teamwork?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場打斗得馬上結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This fight needs to end now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然他們會把我們兩個都送去地表喂蟑螂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or else they'll feed us both to the Roaches on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯現在不會改變規則的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius isn't gonna change the rules now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要知道該問誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You just have to know who to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場打斗讓我覺得無聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This fight bores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證它會以令人興奮的方式結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I assure you it will end in a most thrilling fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錫納拉  讓守衛多扔些武器進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sinara, have the guards throw in more weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在缺少武器\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lack of weapons is not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來看毀滅者戰斗的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I came to see the Destroyer fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這種過氣的老古董\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not some ancient has-been.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕必須要失一命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid a life is owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個神盾局特工送到地表去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Send the Agent of S.H.I.E.L.D. to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維羅尼辛會比看膩了的觀眾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Vrellnexians ‭will have much more use for her
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更想見到她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than your weary audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送這個女人類去地表電梯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Escort the human woman to the surface lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是  你的朋友只是拖延了必然之事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, your friend just delayed the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能逃過蟑螂之口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one can escape the Roaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過那個男孩嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you seen the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗林特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Flint?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can't say I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.21,0:23:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在這層混\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a total floor rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能去了任何地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把他藏起來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...you could be hiding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什么要那樣做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在儀式上看到你們在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I saw you together at the ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他道別來著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}offering the boy last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  弗林特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen, Flint --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能給我找到別人找不到的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he gets me things no one else can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安慰那孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Giving the kid a pep talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想穩定我的商務關系\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was me just keeping my business relationship on the steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我發現你對我有所隱瞞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I find ‭you're keeping things from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后果會很嚴重\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there will be consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We done here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我還沒有擁有超能力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, how come I don't have my powers yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.53,0:24:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經擁有了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.59,0:24:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是還沒有顯現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It just hasn't revealed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力用了多久才出現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How long did yours take?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.34,0:24:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那簡直是場災難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, it was a total disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我三周前因為吃魚湯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I crusted over three weeks earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和墨西哥卷餅而結了殼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}after eating fish soup and tacos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.44,0:24:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥卷餅是什么\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are tacos?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.12,0:24:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么鬼未來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What the hell kind of future is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥卷餅是種食物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tacos are a food.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.23,0:24:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我跟自己說  我是在做夢呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anyways, I had told myself this was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.37,0:25:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我堂弟弗朗西斯科來了電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then ‭my cousin Francisco calls
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.01,0:25:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他媽媽出了事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with bad news about his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很難過  就去拿瓶啤酒  然后一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was upset, so I went to get a beer, and -- whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又回到了沙發上  啤酒已經在手里了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm back on my couch, beer in one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.19,0:25:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意識到  我需要個瓶起子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I realize I need a bottle opener,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.49,0:25:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又一下  我又回到沙發上了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and whoosh again -- I'm back on my couch,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓶起子已經拿在另一只手里了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}bottle opener in the other hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.89,0:25:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是怎么回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did you think was happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.37,0:25:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心跳得好快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My heart was beating so fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.83,0:25:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為是有人在我酒里放了可卡因\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought someone ‭had put cocaine in my beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.31,0:25:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那個啊  大毒梟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dial it back, Escobar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.31,0:25:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好擔心  就叫堂弟弗朗西斯科過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got so worried, I told my cousin Francisco to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.84,0:25:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他花了好幾小時勸我別去接受驅魔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He spent countless hours talking me out of an exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.77,0:25:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這故事很有趣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is a great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.94,0:25:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯肯定會想親耳聽到的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Pretty sure Kasius is gonna want to hear that for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為這讀心人出一萬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}10,000 for the telepath!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.03,0:25:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯不需要錢  他想要的是武器\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius doesn't need money -- he wants weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五門科文里恩大炮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Five Culverian Blasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.55,0:25:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拍賣  卡拉巴夫人  不是跳蚤市場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is an auction, Lady Karaba, not a flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.20,0:25:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著你沒用的玩具回你來的那個泥坑去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take your useless toys back to the mudpits you crawled out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.51,0:25:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了二位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My apologies to you both,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.80,0:25:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能賣掉這名異人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I cannot in good faith sell this Inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.63,0:26:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想什么呢  卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What dense thought rattles in your brain, Kasius?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想憑白被人撩撥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I wanted a tease,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.50,0:26:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去基特森的妓院了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would have visited the brothels of Kitson.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.52,0:26:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你壓抑的欲望與我無關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your pent-up desires do not concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.44,0:26:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于我的理由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As to my reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.81,0:26:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你愿自己跟客人們說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you would care to illuminate our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.29,0:26:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  求你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.99,0:26:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有下次了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.47,0:26:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了  求你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was wrong. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.17,0:26:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前問毀滅者是否有其他人跟她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You see, Ben was present when I asked the Destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.69,0:26:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同穿越時間時  本也在場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if others had traveled through time with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.66,0:26:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她堅稱我的仆人是唯一一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She insisted that my servant was the only one,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.50,0:26:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這并非實話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which turned out to be untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.05,0:26:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯  不怪他  卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius, th-- ‭it's not his fault. Kasius!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.25,0:26:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他撒謊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.36,0:26:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說  這不會影響他的出售\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Normally, that would not preclude him from being sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.81,0:26:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次  他是對我撒謊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only in this instance, that lie was told to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.30,0:26:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有必要嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.01,0:26:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓哪個買家管教他好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Make one of the buyers discipline him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.91,0:27:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是最能理解的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You of all people must understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.37,0:27:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有榮譽感的人  怎能容忍他的奴隸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No man of honor can allow the tongues of his slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.65,0:27:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此公然撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to lie so boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  這要怪我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the one -- I am the one to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.39,0:27:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不是本  -或許吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Not Ben! - ‭Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.40,0:27:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他沒那么有價值\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he's far less valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.75,0:27:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怪自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.19,0:27:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.99,0:27:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.47,0:27:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望  這個展示更合你的胃口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hopefully, you found this display more to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.31,0:27:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來早了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}{\*}You're home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.51,0:27:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為又是叫我來做報告呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thought I was getting called up for another damn report.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.35,0:27:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  我的經理是想告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But turns out, my manager just wanted to let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個拖曳船的飛行員在角斗場里戰斗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that a Trawler pilot was fighting in The Crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.35,0:27:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-梅  -她沒事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- May. - ‭Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.09,0:27:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會用"沒事"來形容一個被丟去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"All right's" not a word I would use for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.42,0:27:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂蟑螂的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who was chucked out as Roach food.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.66,0:28:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許該說  "一小口"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Morsel," maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.56,0:28:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  你該告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now it's time you tell me why
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.02,0:28:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個為什么會沒有生物表\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the three of you didn't have any Metrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.24,0:28:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是從過去穿越來拯救世界的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We came from the past to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.09,0:28:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you -- you speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.10,0:28:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預言嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the Prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.16,0:28:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然是個土包子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, look, I may be a rube,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.86,0:28:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有蠢貨才會相信那套預言的蠢話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but only dumb rubes believe in that prophecy nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.01,0:28:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但等我把你們四個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Though I will be a rich rube
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.10,0:28:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給了卡塞亞斯  我就會有錢了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}once I turn you four in to Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.98,0:28:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我們交出去  我們就死定了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You turn us in, we're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.05,0:28:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.03,0:28:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那死變態給我錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Once that creepy son of a bitch pays me off,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.92,0:28:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管他拿你們怎么辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he can do whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.99,0:28:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, being dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.39,0:28:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還是你們最好的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...might be your best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.97,0:29:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遺憾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.05,0:29:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本救了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ben saved my life --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.59,0:29:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he saved both of our lives --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.91,0:29:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯卻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and Kasius just...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.07,0:29:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么殺了他  而我只能看著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}murdered him while I stood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.63,0:29:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做不了什么的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There was nothing you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.28,0:29:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你得排隊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you'll have to get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.69,0:29:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在能聽到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you can hear now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.28,0:29:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲茲騙卡塞亞斯開啟了我的聽力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fitz tricked Kasius into turning my hearing back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.63,0:29:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-菲茲怎么會在這兒  -我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- How is Fitz even here? - ‭I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.46,0:29:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然就冒了出來  還有自己的飛船\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He just showed up out of nowhere with his own spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.12,0:29:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a baller move.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有他那副賞金獵人的樣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not to mention the whole bounty-hunter look he's rocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.80,0:29:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是更喜歡他穿羊毛衫的樣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I still prefer him in cardigans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.97,0:29:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他在計劃什么嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you have any idea what he's planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.79,0:29:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}‭Yeah, I'm not sure, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.62,0:29:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒撈著機會講話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We haven't had a moment to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:29:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他似乎是來買我們的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}though it would seem he's here to purchase us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.66,0:29:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒成功呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.26,0:30:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有把刀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.48,0:30:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至于吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.77,0:30:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒多少刀具可選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, there was limited cutlery to choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.78,0:30:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是說我們的計劃  我們得想辦法合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, with our plan. We have to figure out a way to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.93,0:30:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯必須在打斗開始后關閉抑制器\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kasius has to turn my Inhibitor off before the fight starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.54,0:30:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到時再行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can make our move then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.64,0:30:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要打誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who are you facing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可犧牲的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someone disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.30,0:30:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲茲肯定會準備好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure Fitz will be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.31,0:30:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here we are again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.50,0:30:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對抗世界\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Us against the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.21,0:30:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  有情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You must hurry. There's a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.71,0:30:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有麻煩了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.67,0:31:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.17,0:31:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人來向卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someone new has arrived to acquire
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.28,0:31:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,購買世界毀滅者了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the Destroyer of Worlds from Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.90,0:31:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我還有錢嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someone more wealthy than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.50,0:31:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也更可怕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And more feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.24,0:31:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哥哥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么卡塞亞斯讓人在樓下打斗  吉爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why does Kasius have people fighting downstairs, Grill?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.91,0:31:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找樂子的游戲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All part of the fun and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.49,0:31:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他不會選你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's just hope he doesn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.52,0:31:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是個孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.98,0:31:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始覺得  澤夫并不該死的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm starting to think that Zev didn't deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.92,0:31:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是你女朋友陷害了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That maybe your girlfriend set him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.30,0:31:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不非得把你們完好無損地交上去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing says that I gotta turn you in cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.65,0:31:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許  我該繼續電電你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, you know, maybe I will just watch you sizzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  小子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, knock it off, junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.69,0:32:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道怎么控制  -那就想辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I don't know how. - ‭Well, you figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.22,0:32:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗林特  看著我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Flint, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.53,0:32:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的天賦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is your gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.16,0:32:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以控制它的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.13,0:32:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  否則我就開槍了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You stop it, or I will stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.46,0:32:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塞亞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}{\*}Kasius.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.13,0:32:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么聽說你哥哥來買毀滅者了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this about your brother coming for the Destroyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.30,0:32:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you'd excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.72,0:33:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多棒啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.26,0:33:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我母星過來路程遙遠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The journey from my home world is significant,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.46,0:33:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親一定是非常看重\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so Father must be quite serious
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.62,0:33:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會派福奈克親自來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if he sent Faulnak in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.71,0:33:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是鬧著玩的  我向你保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm also serious, and I guarantee you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.49,0:33:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這兒的路程要更遙遠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have traveled a much longer journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.64,0:33:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請到你  我非常榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it has been a privilege having you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.42,0:33:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.97,0:33:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得到毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not if I don't get the Destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.57,0:33:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保證過我會有機會競價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You promised me a chance to make an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.21,0:33:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我樂意提供這個機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which I look forward to entertaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.86,0:33:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是建議你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}though I would encourage you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.82,0:33:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮我其他的異人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to consider one of my other Inhumans.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.68,0:33:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來并不順利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That did not appear to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.66,0:33:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望其他的事不會再出錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's hope the rest does.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.75,0:33:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.91,0:33:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有件事需要你去做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's one last thing I need you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.09,0:34:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的命運近在眼前  錫納拉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our fate is soon at hand, Sinara.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.18,0:34:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很榮幸你能到場  哥哥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is an honor to have you join us, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人類糞坑有什么榮幸可言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is no honor to be found in this human cesspool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.89,0:34:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你還是來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yet here you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.85,0:34:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有什么東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There must be something of worth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.62,0:34:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得你如此遠道而來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for you to travel such a great distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.66,0:34:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來僅僅是因為父親有命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm only here ‭because of Father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.96,0:34:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興父親派了你來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It pleases to hear Father sent you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.19,0:34:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最信任的信使\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}his most trusted messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.63,0:34:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個毀滅者最好如你所言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This Destroyer had better be what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.75,0:35:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我會很樂意提醒你我發火時的各種樣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or I'll gladly remind you of the many shapes my anger takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.91,0:35:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.75,0:35:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一向急于展示\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were always quick to offer a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.67,0:35:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許現在  我也可以展示一番了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps now I can present one of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅者將要跟我最\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Destroyer is set to battle
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.60,0:35:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害的一名異人對決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}one of my most prized Inhumans --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.37,0:35:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no desire
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.24,0:35:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的本土試驗品打斗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to see one of your ‭homegrown experiments fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.46,0:35:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅者必須面對一名克里戰士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Destroyer must face a Kree warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.60,0:35:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的跟班就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your stray shall suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.28,0:35:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但錫納拉并沒做好戰斗準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But Sinara is not prepared for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.13,0:35:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是你最厲害的戰士嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is she not your greatest warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.45,0:35:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你躲在她身后的樣子  讓人這么覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You cower behind her as though she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.57,0:35:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps I have misjudged
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.96,0:35:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再想獲得父親的認可了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you no longer seek Father's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.99,0:35:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.45,0:35:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錫納拉會樂意出戰的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sinara would be honored to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.19,0:36:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.58,0:36:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這很突然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...I understand this is sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.66,0:36:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是極佳的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it presents a tremendous opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.03,0:36:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所努力爭取的一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything I have been striving for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.81,0:36:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都看這一場打斗了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is but one fight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決一死戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.19,0:36:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is what has been promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.07,0:36:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have every confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.32,0:36:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會讓我們看到精彩的場面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that you will provide us all a great spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.29,0:36:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待不下去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  外面太危險了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold on. It's too dangerous out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.52,0:36:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也比就盯著我剛殺的人好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's better than staring at the guy I just killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.04,0:36:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I knew him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.49,0:36:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我最好的客人之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was one of my best customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.14,0:37:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時還多給我一兩個代幣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even gave me spare tokens from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.14,0:37:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾的事不能怪你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened to Grill is not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.52,0:37:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別無選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.04,0:37:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當時要殺我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was gonna kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.90,0:37:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克和我  我們去找泰絲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, Mack and I -- we're gonna go find Tess,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后帶你上一架拖曳船  好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we're gonna get you on a Trawler, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.47,0:37:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子該在打球\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kid should be playing ball
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.39,0:37:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或競選學生會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or running for student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是生活委員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or class treasurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.49,0:37:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這么明確  -我做了三屆呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- That's pretty specific. - ‭Ah, served three terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.83,0:37:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個很對金錢負責的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a pretty ‭financially responsible dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.00,0:37:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰絲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.39,0:37:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不肯交出弗林特他們就殺了她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They killed her because she wouldn't give up Flint.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.35,0:37:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經死了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.13,0:37:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在只能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only thing we can do now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.00,0:37:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓弗林特不會落得同樣的下場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is try to keep Flint from meeting that same end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.63,0:37:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.15,0:37:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  壓軸戲開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, our main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.70,0:37:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河系最致命的力量之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One of the galaxy's deadliest forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.16,0:37:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今晚  她將為取悅你們而戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yet tonight, she fights for your enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.68,0:37:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的朋友們  我向你們獻上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dear friends, may I present to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震波女  世界毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...Quake, the Destroyer of Worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.63,0:38:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小丫頭就是你的毀滅者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This puny girl is your Destroyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.70,0:38:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太急著下判斷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your rush to judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.81,0:38:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一向是你的短處  哥哥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}has always been a shortcoming, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.06,0:38:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先關閉毀滅者的抑制器\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Allow me to switch off the Destroyer's Inhibitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.98,0:38:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就能看到她的真本事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then you shall see her true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.54,0:38:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  在那之前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course, before I unleash her,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.36,0:38:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得采取防護措施\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we must take precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.07,0:38:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做一番開幕講話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you care to give the opening commencement?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.90,0:39:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的跟班不想再接受命令了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seems your stray is done taking orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.43,0:39:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  你個藍妖婊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, you freaky blue bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.94,0:39:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.45,0:39:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is for Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.97,0:40:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.95,0:40:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛  攔下他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Guards, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.59,0:41:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再不會離開你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm never leaving you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.21,0:41:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就娶我吧  菲茲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then marry me, Fitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.86,0:41:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.40,0:41:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  來吧  我扶你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, come on. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.76,0:41:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  我想說  我之前求婚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Also, um, just to say, I did propose earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.76,0:41:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卡塞亞斯關閉了你的聽力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...when Kasius ‭had your hearing turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.06,0:41:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.12,0:41:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I -- Seriously, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.11,0:41:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}{\*}Hello, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.59,0:41:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.69,0:41:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個克里人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am a Kree.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.21,0:41:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是  兄弟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As I have always been, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.68,0:41:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在往哪去嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.19,0:41:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那兒的人回不來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People don't come back from there --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.19,0:42:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am not a person.

